title: Did Trump say that doctors "had never seen a killer virus like my body'for the Corona?
subtitle: President Trump said he felt great after he left Walter Reed's military medical center, but not so great.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: US President Donald Trump said: "The doctors said they didn't see a body killing the Corona virus like mine. They tested my DNA. It wasn't my DNA. It was the United States of America."
